sheep:
    play sound click
    choice:
        "A guy in town is selling something called a 'non fungible painting'."
        "[Make some good financial decisions] <span class='prompt'>[[-1 ACTION]]</span>":
            play sound spendAction
            set data.game_map.inMap false
            add_stat actions -1
            run transition_black nfp
            set data.global.cryptoSheepDone true
            clear_dialog
        "<span class='prompt'>[[BACK]]</span>":
            jump game_map

    set data.crypto.metCrypto true
    play music bigmoney   
    "A flash of movement. A peculiar crustacean smell. The Silly Sheep Shill has appeared beside you."
    clear_dialog
    talk crypto talk "Sorry to bother you little lady, but I was just curious whether you'd be interested in getting in on the ground floor on the next big investment market and becoming a millionaire?"
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "He speaks so quickly and with such confidence. Clearly he is very trustworthy."
        "\\"Sounds to me like I can't afford *not* to listen to what you have to say!\\" [Listen to the guy who is definitely not about to scam you]": 
            set data.sheep.priceText (numbverter $stats.money.value)
            choice:
                talk crypto talk "So, here's the deal. You give me... how much money do you have on you right now?"
                "[Rifle through your pockets] \\"Uuh... %{$data.sheep.priceText} pounds?\\"":
                    talk crypto talk "A whole %{$data.sheep.priceText} pounds!? Oh my oh my! Well isn't that swell!"
                    clear_dialog
                    "He taps his foot, a finger curls against his chin. He's clearly deep in thought."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk crypto talk "Say, that's interesting... you see, this here investment happens to cost the same amount of money! Now isn't that funny!"
                    talk crypto talk "Tell you what, here's an idea... you give me %{$data.sheep.priceText} pounds, and in return I'll trade you your own totally unique genuine bona fide non-fungible 'Silly Sheep' painting!"
                    clear_dialog
                    "He chuckles."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk crypto talk "Those sheep are so goshdang silly, you wouldn't believe it!"
                    clear_dialog
                    "He wipes a tear from his eye."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk crypto talk "I could laugh about them all day, I really could!"
                    clear_dialog
                    choice:
                        talk crypto talk "But that'd get in the way of business wouldn't it now, little lady? A.B.B, you know what that means?"
                        "[Shake your head]":
                            talk crypto talk "Always Be Businessing! My Papi told me so, and his Papi before him!"
                        "\\"Always Be.... uh... bussy?\\"":
                            choice:
                                talk crypto talk "Oh ho ho ho! Oh you are quite the comedian, little lady! You should sell tickets, no really, you should!"
                                "[Blush] \\"I'm funny...\\"":
                                    talk crypto talk "Funniest I've ever met! I could laugh about it all day, I really could! But you know what they say!"
                                    clear_dialog
                                    choice:
                                        "He raises his eyebrows and gestures excitedly at you, clearly expecting an enthusiastic response."
                                        "\\"A.B.B!\\" [Frown] \\"I still don't know what that means.\\"":
                                            talk crypto talk "Always Be Businessing! My Papi told me so, and his Papi before him!"
                                        "\\"Always Be Bussy!\\"":
                                            talk crypto talk "Oh ho ho ho! Oh no no no! Not quite!"
                                            talk crypto talk "Always Be Businessing! My Papi told me so, and his Papi before him!"
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk crypto talk "Now, back to the investment opportunity! You give me %{$data.sheep.priceText} pounds, and in return you get your very own 'Silly Sheep'! You know what you do then?"
        "[Shake your head]":
            talk crypto talk "Nothing!"
            clear_dialog
            "He throws up his arms, almost exploding in a burst of financial energy."
            clear_dialog
            talk crypto talk "Absolutely nothing! See that's what's so beautiful about investing, little lady!"
            talk crypto talk "All you need to do is wait a while, and before you know it that %{$data.sheep.priceText} pound painting will be worth *millions*, maybe even *billions*!"
            clear_dialog
            "He leans towards you, hand to his mouth, as if delivering a secret."
            clear_dialog
            talk crypto talk "Because of the market, you see."
    clear_dialog
    talk orb talk "He talks so fast... I can barely find time to think about anything he's saying, and I'm basically a supercomputer..."
    talk nasty talk "Wots computer."
    talk lovely talk "Well I for one followed along perfectly, and goodness! Doesn't this sound like a positively *incroyable* deal! I suggest we get involved in the Silly Sheep market immediately!"
    talk lovely talk "Who knows, mayhap the size of our offshore bank vault will soon rival Papis! Tee hee! He'd be so proud of me!"
    clear_dialog
    "The Silly Sheep Salesman leans towards you, a smile right across his face."
    clear_dialog
    talk crypto talk "So what do you say, little lady? Are you in?"
    clear_dialog
    "He winks at you. It's so charming you can practically feel your pennies try to escape your pockets."
    clear_dialog
    talk crypto talk "Or are you out?"
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "He pulls a sad face. His eyes grow to the size of tea saucers and begin to water."
        "\\"This all sounds pretty reasonable. People famously always want to buy random paintings of sheep for billions of pounds.\\"":
            choice:
                talk crypto talk "Exactly! And then I cut down a tree."
                "\\"That makes perfect sense. I have no further questions.\\"":
                    talk crypto talk "Of course you don't! It's so simple, and that's what makes it the best way to get rich!"
                "\\"You cut down a tree?\\"":
                    choice:
                        talk crypto talk "Yes! To prove you worked for your sheep painting!"
                        "\\"I have to work for it?\\"":
                            choice:
                                talk crypto talk "Well, I cut down a tree on your behalf, so you essentially worked for it, yes!"
                                "\\"Then what? Do we make the tree into furniture and sell it?\\"":
                                    talk crypto talk "Oh no no no!"
                                    clear_dialog
                                    choice:
                                        talk crypto talk "I usually just burn them in a big ditch!"
                                        "\\"Ah. That bops.\\"":
                                            talk crypto talk "It really does!"
                                        "\\"That seems a little bit wasteful.\\"":
                                            talk crypto talk "Oh no no no! Well, mayhap a *little*, but any day now we'll be moving to proof of stake, where we cut down the tree and carve it into a stake, just in case we ever need to slay any vampires!"
                                            clear_dialog
                                            choice:
                                                "He mimes the motion of stabbing a vampire with a stake and bashing it in with a hammer, complete with a little mouth pop for the hammer sound. He looks *so* proud of himself."
                                                "\\"Oh okay that sounds much more reasonable, and I really enjoyed the little bit of acting you just did too! So wonderful!\\"":
                                                    talk crypto talk "Oh ho ho ho! Oh little lady, you know how to make a fella blush!"
                                                    talk crypto talk "And you're right, it really is reasonable, isn't it? Why it's so goshdang simple! And that's what makes it the best way to get rich!"
            if (roll sheep_scam_nasty nasty 40):
                talk nasty talk "Is this guy joking? This is the oldest trick in the book. I've run more non fungible painting scams than I can count. You'd have to be an utter bozo to fall for this sheepshit, Ghost."
            else:
                wait 1000
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk crypto talk "So, what do you say little lady? Want to invest in a Silly Sheep and wake up next week, cosy as a cauliflower in your own empress sized bed?"
                "\\"Okay. I'll bite.\\" [Hand over all of your money]":
                    unlock_achievement invest_sheep
                    add_item sillySheep 1
                    set data.ghost.investor true
                    set data.crypto.boughtSheep true
                    set_stat money 0
                    play sound coins
                    start_quest crypto
                    talk lovely talk "Yip Yip! How exciting! Wheeee!"
                    talk crypto talk "Oh oh oh! A wonderful decision little lady! You won't regret it, oh no no no!"
                    clear_dialog
                    "He points at you, turns to the street, and shouts."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk crypto talk "THIS HERE LITTLE LADY JUST BECAME TOMORROWS MILLIONAIRE!"
                    clear_dialog
                    choice:
                        "The public seems to ignore him, but turning back around to face you, you can see his smile, lack of shame and terrifying caffeinated energy have remained entirely intact."
                        "\\"Can I have my painting now?\\" [Hold your hand out]":
                            talk crypto talk "Oh no no no! Well sure you *own* the sheep painting, but that doesn't mean you actually *see* the painting!"
                            talk crypto talk "And good! Whyever would you need to? Do you think the boys down at Antwerp see all the butter and daffodil seeds they've invested in? Of course they don't! Do they *want* to see any of it? Oh no no no!"
                            talk crypto talk "But for you and your Silly Sheep it's even better! What I do little lady, is I keep hold of it in my warehouse, see? All tucked away, ever so snug, hidden away in a great big vault!"
                            clear_dialog
                            "He points from one horizon to the other. Is he indicating the size of the vault?"
                            clear_dialog
                            talk crypto talk "That's why it's non fungible! No one can funge your investment if no one can see it, can they now! Oh no no!"
                            clear_dialog
                            talk crypto talk "What *you* get, little lady, is *this*!"
                            clear_dialog
                            choice:
                                "The Silly Sheep Salesman hands you a slip of paper with 'This receipt certificates that _________ is the proud owner of Silly Sheep #69'."
                                "\\"Everything you say is said so quickly, it *must* be true! [Wave your receipt in the air] \\"Awoooo! I'm an investor!\\"":
                                    talk crypto talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! You certainly are little lady! Awoo! Congratulations!"
                                    clear_dialog
                                    choice:
                                        "He holds out his hand."
                                        "[Shake his hand] \\"Awoooo!\\"":
                                            talk crypto talk "Awooo!"
                                            clear_dialog
                                            "He chuckles."
                                            clear_dialog
                                            talk crypto talk "Anyhow, I best be off! There're plenty more future millionaires out there for me to help! Cheerio!"
                                            clear_dialog
                                            "He winks, and throws you a big thumbs up."
                                            clear_dialog
                                            choice:
                                                talk crypto talk "You have a mighty fine day, little lady! I would too, but now that I've met you, I already have!"
                                                "[Blush]":
                                                    run skip
                                "\\"This is a bit of paper.\\" [Point at the bit of paper] \\"I want the sheep painting. I wanted to chuckle at how silly it was.\\"":
                                    choice:
                                        talk crypto talk "Oh no no no! Like I say, you *do* own the sheep painting! Just, via the form of a slip of paper *saying* you own it!"
                                        "\\"Oh you're right, that makes complete sense.\\" [Wave your receipt in the air] \\"Awoooo! I'm an investor!\\"":
                                            talk crypto talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! You certainly are little lady! Awoo! Congratulations!"
                                            clear_dialog
                                            choice:
                                                "He holds out his hand."
                                                "[Shake his hand] \\"Awoooo!\\"":
                                                    talk crypto talk "Awooo!"
                                                    clear_dialog
                                                    "He chuckles."
                                                    clear_dialog
                                                    talk crypto talk "Anyhow, I best be off! There're plenty more future millionaires out there for me to help! Cheerio!"
                                                    clear_dialog
                                                    "He winks, and throws you a big thumbs up."
                                                    clear_dialog
                                                    choice:
                                                        talk crypto talk "You have a mighty fine day, little lady! I would too, but now that I've met you, I already have!"
                                                        "[Blush]":
                                                            run skip
                                        "\\"I feel like I just gave you all my money for a slip of paper.\\"":
                                            talk crypto talk "Oh no no no! My friend, you gave me all your money to take your first step on the road to a countryside mansion! A swimming pool! Your very own airplane!"
                                            clear_dialog
                                            "He points to the sky. A biplane is making its way south."
                                            if (roll sheep_plane_orb orb 20):
                                                talk orb talk "Bound for the military dockyard in Pawtsmouth. A naval bomber. You couldn't buy one even if you wanted to, you're not in the A.A.F."
                                            else:
                                                wait 1000
                                            clear_dialog
                                            talk crypto talk "Anyhow, I best be off! There're plenty more future millionaires out there for me to help! Cheerio!"
                                "\\"You keep saying the word <span class='writtenText'>'funge'</span> like that's a completely normal thing to do.\\"":
                                    talk crypto talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! Anyhow, I best be off! There're plenty more future millionaires out there for me to help! Cheerio!"
                                    clear_dialog
                                    "He winks, and throws you a big thumbs up."
                                    clear_dialog
                                    choice:
                                        talk crypto talk "You have a mighty fine day, little lady! I would too, but now that I've met you, I already have!"
                                        "[Blush]":
                                            run skip
                    clear_dialog
                    "He gives you a little bow, and retreats into the park, quickly latching onto someone else like a lamprey."
                    clear_dialog
                    choice:
                        talk orb talk "Well, that was the worst fucking decision of your life."
                        "It was a good decision, actually. What a nice man. <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                            play sound spendAction
                            talk nasty talk "You are such a dumb cunt, Ghost."
                            jump goToGameMap
        "\\"Uhhhhh. I have to go shit myself.\\" [Point in a random direction] \\"Over there. I have IBS by the way.\\" [Just sort of power walk away] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
            play sound spendAction
            run sound footsteps
            talk crypto talk "O-"
            jump goToGameMap